POE-Wheel-Sendfile version 0.02
===============================

POE::Wheel::Sendfile extends POE::Wheel::ReadWrite and adds the
possibility of using the sendfile system call to transfer data as
efficiently.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  POE
  Sys::Sendfile

